                <div class="card-body text-center">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Remote-Controlled Car</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Fun and fast remote-controlled car for kids and adults.</p>
                    <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07RT78G48" class="btn btn-primary">Shop Now</a>
                </div>
